План был крутой: подняться через Голубую горку на вершину #большойтакмак, потом перейти с него на #малыйтакмак, выйти в #бобровыйлогкрасноярск и на канатке спуститься вниз. Ну а там пешком дотопать до машины, брошенной на Базаихе в районе Восточного входа на #Столбы

Пришлось весь обратный путь проделать пешком - по скользкому снегу и сырой прошлогодней траве с ручьями. Как-то не аккуратно для моей ноги, конечно. Посмотрим, что скажет Каа... То есть спортивный доктор, конечно.

🇨🇲 For many years I always thought this Cameroon shirt with a more angular interpretation of a lion on the front than the shirt I had already was not as nice and so ignored it. Over the years I've realised I was wrong and somehow this incarnation feels more African and cool, and I've been fortunate that the shirt is still widely available to correct my mistake of not buying when it was current. As always I love the double badge and centralised Puma logo... using them in the eye sockets of the lion is a masterstroke. The real beauty of this though is in the little dots running down the sleeve and used to make up the lion's face in a sort of Roy Lichtenstein homage which I'd never noticed either when I didn't rate the design, or when I'd come round to loving it. The Cameroon flag colours around the collar matches up nicely with the badges as well and just have no excuse as to why I wasn't in love with this from day one of its release. I missed Cameroon at the last World Cup after years of liking them but thinking I wouldn't miss them. I feel Cameroon were the archetypal African nation at a World Cup for anyone of my generation (don't comment to say it was Nigeria, you're wrong), and certainly the standard bearer for kit designs before kit design became important - whilst almlost every African nation is now kitted out magnificently every year, Cameroon were doing it before it sold. caption:
Los pumas, también conocidos como leones de montaña 🏞️ son felinos estrictamente carnívoros que cuentan con una amplia distribución, pueden vivir en hábitats como montañas, bosques, desiertos y humedales. 
1.	Su tamaño puede variar con su ubicación ya que los individuos cerca del ecuador son más pequeños que los individuos cerca de los polos 🌎
2.	Los machos pueden llegar a pesar entre 52-100 kilogramos mientras que las hembras tienen un peso entre 64-141 kilogramos.
3.	Como son crepusculares, requieren de una excelente vista para cazar de noche 👀
4.	Pueden medir entre 86-155 centímetros y su cola llega a medir entre 60-97 centímetros 📏
5.	Sus patas traseras son más grandes y musculosas que sus patas delanteras para darles un gran poder de salto.

Si quieres más información consulta las siguientes fuentes 👇🏼:

Артикул 22743/NIKE

Баскетбольные кроссовки Nike LeBron XVIII - именная модель знаменитого баскетболиста NBA Леброна Джеймса. Пара изготовлена с учетом его пожеланий и предпочтений. Верх модели выполнен из плотного текстиля. Этот материал отлично дышит. Система шнуровки лаконично вписывается в образ, а также плотно фиксирует стопу, что немаловажно во время игры. В области пятки имеется специальная петля, которая обеспечивает удобство при надевании. Внутри модели установлены мягкие вставки, которые придают комфорт во время использования. Стелька отлично дышит. Основную часть нагрузок берет на себя воздушный баллон, который расположен в области пятки. Резиновая подметка способна взаимодействовать с разными поверхностями. Также модель имеет кастомную расцветку.

Why did Neymar start the match from the bench?

—🎙Mauricio Pochettino:

«Neymar caught a cold and he had a little fever. He was not in the best shape to start a match. If the game had been ended before he wouldn't have come into play. But at 2-2 there were a few minutes left, which is why I put him in because we could go on penalties. That was one of the reasons he was on the bench tonight even though it was a shame he got a yellow card»

To be honest, I feel sorry for him. He played like a selfless warrior. He entered the field with a temperature, received a very controversial yellow card and seems to miss the final (it's not clear yet). He scored an incredibly beautiful and confident penalty, he only played 8 minutes!! During this time, he provided the team with access to the final, but risks missing it due to a yellow card. Neymar is very strong and courageous, I’m very proud of him. Every time on the pitch, he proves that he deserves to be called the best. And again injustice found him. Next match on May 16 against Reims. I hope they take care of Neymar!

caption:
One would say... Really... both tires flat , really... and yes that is the god damn reality of things.. I have no tubes lying around so couldn't use the bike to warm up for my long run today... and it is a bank holiday, so can't buy new ones today. 
Well nomatter, just had to run fairly slow until I got warmed up... 
Yesterday I had one hour bike and weight session, but skipped squat because I wanted to run 10+ today. 
I heard a podcast yesterday #atleterudenfilter by @louiburgaard , with a Danish marathon runner which reminded me, about something I already know but tend to forget. Training long distance run isn't about speed but about kilometers. So ran a 6.minute pace per km for 11k today.. instead of the 5.35 which I usually do, running that route... 
Once again I am sitting comparing myself with back then, when I trained for ironman, and once again I have to remind myself I am rebooting my training and I am nowhere near my former run pace and I don't need to be.. I train so I can do a half ironman. I wanna be in half ironman shape... Not to compete, not to be faster than my first half ironman... Just because I like the training and I wanna be able to, if I suddenly feel the urge to do a race... 
I simply just love the training.. Well once again it rained my whole run 🌧 but still...

Es interesante como todo llega a su tiempo justo.
Trabajar este Centro Ceremonial (como cada encargo de bordado) algo vino a trabajar en mi interior, mi raíz, mi firmeza , mi seguridad. 
🌱 Bordarlo y ritualizarlo fue en ese momento (que perdura hasta hoy, porque todos los trabajos profundos que nos animamos a hacer en nosotres mismes perdura por mucho tiempo 🕝) un regalo para mi. 
♦️Y hoy mostrárselos (finalmente) también no es casual; porque estoy aterrizando nuevamente en estas tierra 🛸…. trabajando fuertemente mi enraizar, colocando mis manos en la tierra y sembrando para que una vez más este territorio me reconozca como parte.  ~ Cuando viajamos durante un tiempo (fisicamente o andamos muy volado en la vida) nuestro chacra raíz  puede debilitarse… y que este se encuentre “debilitado” de alguna manera repercute en el tiempo que conlleva materializar nuestras ideas e intenciones ~ tanto así como a una planta : sin raíz firme nunca dará flor.🌾
 Por eso en este nuevo aterrizar, lo primero es “hacer tierra” hacer raíz, cuidar de ella . Ser la puma que reconoce su territorio y vive ne sus ciclos.

🐅 The Onitsuka Tiger Colorado 85 silhouette has been one of the most iconic for collaborations in the past, so we came up with something different, a trading card game that has been here for a long time, Yu-Gi-Oh!, this colourway is inspired by "a powerful engine of destruction, virtually invincible", the legendary Blue Eyes White Dragon.
This colourway has been designed directly from the SDK-E001 Blue Eyes White Dragon card in hand.
The upper features a cracked white/blue leather, blue flat grain leather overlays, the tiger stripes are made with a synthetic enamel finish so as the heel tab and a gradient colour on the rubber outsole.
On the removable insole you'll find the OG artwork printed with its ATK and DEF, as well as the level 8 stars.
There would be so many little details that you'd love on the paper tissue and box.

Materials:
Upper - Cracked Leather 
Toe Cap - Leather
Eyestay - Leather
Side overlays - Suede
Tongue - Nylon
Tiger Stripes - Synthetic 
Lining - Textile
Heel Tab - Synthetic 
Heel counter - Leather

Responsável pela contratação de Dudu em 2015, Alexandre Mattos, ex-diretor de futebol do Palmeiras, não esconde seu carinho pelo Alviverde nas redes sociais e sempre comenta e publica posts relacionados ao clube. 

Nesta semana, em alguns comentários, o dirigente afirmou que o atacante, ídolo da torcida, está voltando – o que pode acontecer caso o Al-Duhail não exerça a opção de compra junto ao Verdão após um ano de empréstimo.

Ao comentar uma publicação postada pelo zagueiro Gustavo Gómez, Alexandre Mattos recebeu um pedido especial de um torcedor: “Convence o Dudu a voltar, por favor, Mattos”. O ex-diretor respondeu: “Está voltando”. Em outro post, outro torcedor comentou: “volta para o Palmeiras e faz sua mágica para trazer o Dudu de volta!”, e o dirigente novamente respondeu: “está chegando”.

Came across this family fun trail while hiking to my Elkmont campsite in the GSM. 

Want to include the entire family on a very exciting hiking trail that will reward you with some amazing views and have you away from the crowds?

Well look no further my friends as the Great Smoky Mountains NP has provided you with Clingmans Dome Bypass Trail! 

This Family Friendly trail has grades along this trail that will challenge children but their short durations make them doable, and the breathtaking views atop Clingmans Dome make them worth it.

The trailhead is located at the Clingmans Dome parking lot where the Forney Ridge Trail begins. While the paved trail to Clingmans Dome might be easier, it can be very crowded. If you are looking for solitude as you start your adventures on the AT, this is the quieter option for getting to the long trail. 

The Clingmans Dome Bypass Trail drops .2 miles from the parking lot before coming to a junction. The trail goes off to the right and begins to climb uphill towards the Appalachian Trail (AT). The trail is rocky through this section, but views of some high elevation meadows are offered on the left side of the trail. The tree cover quickly disappears due to the death of the Fraser firs in the area. The trail climbs gently until it meets up with the Appalachian Trail (AT) .3 miles west of Clingmans Dome observation tower. At this junction, excellent views of Elkmont and Sugarland Mountain are off to the north and west. 

Once you reach the junction, you have several options. Off to your left, you can explore the 

Appalachian Trail as it makes its way toward Silers Bald. If you turn to the right, you can follow the AT back to Clingmans Dome Observation Tower (and the crowds) and then follow the paved trail back to the parking lot. 

It's a 1.5 mile roundtrip loop, making for a nice day in the mountains.

Shared By: David Hitchcock

Folga de válvulas zero? Porque NÃO se usar! 

SUPER DICA !!!

A folga de válvulas é especificada pelo fabricante do motor levando em conta os materiais de fabricação dos componentes do trem de válvulas (comando, tucho, varetas, balanceiros, reguladores, válvulas e qualquer outra peça que faça parte). Ela serve para compensar a dilatação térmica, pois como é sabido, quando um metal é aquecido seu tamanho aumenta. Essa folga serve justamente para compensar a dilatação das peças quando o motor atinge a temperatura ideal de funcionamento. Quando se regula sem folga, as peças se dilatam e pela falta de compensação, o conjunto fica “grande demais” e resulta em uma válvula que não fecha no momento da explosão, gerando perda de rendimento e outros danos como perda da vedação.  

Sendo assim, regule com a folga recomendada pelo fabricante do motor ou das peças de performance, caso as utilize - geralmente vem um folder com os dados e a medida da folga, como circulado na segunda foto (Valve lash)

O novo manto para jogos em casa do rossonero traz um design que repesenta “a rápida aceleração da cultura da cidade à medida que o Milan se reinventa”. O manto titular do AC Milan para a temporada traz o vermelho como cor predominante e apresenta cinco listras verticais pretas no corpo, em larguras diferentes. A cor é vista novamente nos detalhes laterais e nas axilas (que fazem o modelo lembrar bastante o template da Nike de 2002). Na nuca é escrito “Sempre Milan”. A PUMA estampa o felino na cor branca nas mangas e no lado direito do peito, enquanto o escudo do Milan é colocado no lado esquerdo, em sua versão atual padrão.

Muito tem se falado na volta de Dudu ao Verdão. Eu, particularmente, embora deseje muito que isso aconteça, não acredito nessa volta nesse momento. Isso porque o Al Duhail precisa pagar 6 milhões de euros pela permanência do jogador que foi o destaque da equipe na temporada. Claro que é muito dinheiro, mas levando em consideração que já foram pagos 8 milhões de euros pelo empréstimo de 1 ano e no caso de não aquisição existe uma multa ao próprio jogador de 2,5 milhões de euros, acho praticamente impossível a equipe não exercer a sua preferência na aquisição. Pois estaríamos falando de mais 3,5 milhões de euros por um jogador totalmente diferenciado. Na minha opinião só estão deixando para informar no último momento para atrapalhar o nosso planejamento já que não aceitamos parcelar o referido valor. A única esperança é que com a eliminação da atual equipe de Dudu de todas as competições, a equipe só volta a jogar em setembro.  Enfim, vou torcer pela sua volta desacreditando, se de fato voltar talvez tenha sido umas das melhores negociações nossas dos últimos tempos, pois na atual situação econômica que vivemos receber 8 milhões de euros por um simples empréstimo seria mágico. Volta Dudu!!! Vamos Verdão!!! Juntos somos mais fortes!!! O Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Taupe Haze' apresenta um estilo discreto do design de 1989 de Tinker Hatfield. Um acabamento cinza escuro é aplicado na parte superior, construído a partir de uma mistura de camurça texturizada com couro rachado na gola, na lingueta e no guarda-lamas. Batidas pretas contrastantes pousam nos atacadores, nas asas de plástico e na aba do calcanhar, esta última marcada com o logotipo do Jumpman em relevo. Um segundo ícone do Jumpman é renderizado em infravermelho na etiqueta da língua, combinando com o forro interno da língua. O amortecimento leve é ​​fornecido por uma entressola de PU de dois tons, que abriga uma unidade de ar visível no calcanhar e ar encapsulado no antepé.

5/5 〜  下り止まり迄 : ローファット食 (1,200kcal / 日)
P : 〜125・F : 〜20・C : 〜130
5月の目標 : 2kg減⤵️ 達成🙌
『やるかやらないか』では無く『やる‼️』の一択❗️
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
こんばんは🌝

今日はエニタイムでWスプリット‼️
久し振りにしたなぁ😅

先ずは〜
ベンチプレス…
30kgは一回挙がって次に35kgやってみたらびくともせず😱
トレーナーにも言われたな😅
『35kgはなかなか重たいですよ!』って。
兎に角、ダメ元でもやってみる〜🎶

2回目の時…
レッグプレス終えて次行こうと思ったら男性に声を掛けられアドバイスされちゃった😅

後ろもも効かせる為には ☆♪¥$€%#○+×÷
もう少し足を開いて………
内転筋………
スクワットする時も〜〜だからレッグプレスも〜〜〜……

ほんま突然のことでびっくりした😅
声が小さくて全部は聞き取れんかった💧

有酸素後に少しポージング練習してたんやけど、その時もチラチラ見られてて何か恥ずかしかった😅

今日の食事は完璧👍
これで明日 停滞や増えてたら沼さん導入
もう作って準備🆗

明日は通し勤務🐙
がむしゃらに頑張りまぁす💪

ではでは👋
·
【日々のミッション】
◎ 朝食前の有酸素
◎ 朝食or昼食時にブラックコーヒー☕️
◎ 入浴後のストレッチ
◎ 就寝前にココア生姜白湯
🍀-------------------------------------------------☘️
24/7workoutに通い、約1年で24㎏の減量に成功しました。
アラフィフの私でもしっかりトレーナーについて来たお陰でココまで変わる事が出来ました。
ダイエットは簡単な事ではありません…。
時には辛い事もありますがそれ以上の喜びが待ってます。
年齢なんて関係有りません🎵
是非、一緒に美ボディ目指しませんか⁉️

Что меня безмерно поразило, когда я начала работать в австрийской больнице- это возраст пациентов!
Подавляющее большинство- процентов 75-80- это люди под 90 и за 90. Встретилась за это время и парочка столетних.
Пациентов в возрасте 60-70 мой шеф называет «blüht jung», что в переводе означает «молодой и цветущий».
Но не спешите восхищаться продолжительностью жизни европейцев.
Большинство из них- постояльцы домов престарелых. И не просто престарелых, а тех, кто не может ухаживать за собой, и чьи родственники не захотели тянуть эту ношу.
Большинство из них- в глубокой деменции. Многие вообще витают в какой-то другой реальности и не вступают в контакт с окружающим миром.
При этом в медицинском смысле они всячески ухожены: вставные челюсти и слуховые аппараты, искусственные суставы, имплантированные водители ритма ( для сердца), оперированные катаракты, удаленные все внутренние органы, которые только можно.
При малейшей попытке отправиться к праотцам, их тут же везут в больницу, лечат, реанимируют. Продляют существование.
Если бы не такое количество престарелых пациентов, австрийские врачи давно остались бы без работы.
Для себя я пока не нашла ответа на такой вопрос: нужно ли столь активно лечить пациентов подобного возраста и продлять им существование?
Если примерять ситуацию на себя: будь я в здравом уме и подвижности, наверное, мне хотелось бы жить долго и дождаться внуков/правнуков.
Но быть в 90 лет выжившей из ума, прикованной к постели и на попечении чужих людей мне бы точно не хотелось.
Хотя кто знает, что в головах этих дементных стариков? Может они по-своему счастливы в своём странном мире?
А что вы думаете по этому вопросу?

Keep getting up everyday and trying, because sometimes life turns around and things start falling into place.

Sometimes you have to hit rock bottom to rise up!

Girona 2018/19 Away Shirt courtesy of @umbro — The Catalonian based side Girona wore this effervescent yellow attire in what was to be their second season in Spain’s top Flight ‘La Liga’. Having finished 10th in their La Liga debut in 2017/18, it was always going to be a feat to match it or even top it - Girona failed to do either as they finished 18th in the league and as a result were relegated back to the second tier of Spanish football. Eusebio Sacristán’s men crashed out of the Copa del Rey in the Quarter-Finals after a 7-3 defeat to Real Madrid, however, the Round-of-16 game saw them pull off a shock win via away goals against Atletico Madrid. Girona are part-owned by the City Football Group, the group which own clubs like New York City FC, Mumbai City, Melbourne City and, of course, Manchester City - CFG have a 44.3% stake in the club with Girona Football Group owning another 44.3% in the club, Pere Guardiola, brother of Manchester City Manager Pep Guardiola, is the leader of the Girona Football Group. This information is irrelevant in terms of the shirt in question and the 18/19 La Liga season but I thought it to be intriguing enough to include it in the post.

Here at Quickgrind we make a wide variety of high performance drills, as well as drills for dedicated applications, just like we do for any other type of tool we make. That is what our Infinite Possibilities programme is all about… the right drill, for the right job at the right price.

Our Puma HRSA-TC (through-coolant) and HRSA-D (solid) are the result of extensive work developing the ultimate carbide drills for the economic and secure drilling of tough and difficult materials such as titanium, stainless steels, Nimonic® and other super alloys.

Puma drills can be designed with application-specific helix angle and flute geometries. The flute form geometry, designed especially for long-chipping steels, ensures optimal chip generation characteristics even at low cutting speeds - a tough drill for tough materials.

The through-coolant version ensures perfect penetration and cutting characteristics when machining long-chipping steels. Cutting forces and temperatures are considerably reduced.

These types of materials can result in work-hardening, chip elongation, low thermal conductivity and welding on the tool, but the Puma overcomes these problems. Clever flute design produces optimal chip shape resulting in smooth chip evacuation.

• Shanks to H6 DIN 6535 HA or HB

• Application specific helix angle & flute geometries

• Point geometries & margin options optimised for excellent resistance to tool wear

• Solid carbide micrograin & a choice of coatings (PG shown)

• Through-coolant ensures perfect penetration & cutting characteristics

Don’t forget, we can make virtually any type of drill specifically for your job, whether it is a new design or one you are already running from another manufacturer. We will either design a new drill for you, or we will match the drills you use and optimise the design. That’s Infinite Possibilities.
